HEADWORD: Participant
<hw>Par*tic"i*pant</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>participans</ets>, p. pr. of <ets>participare</ets>: cf. F.
<ets>participant</ets>. See <er>Participate</er>.]</ety> <def>Sharing;
participating; having a share or part.</def>
<rj><au>Bacon.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

