==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Participant
<hw>Par*tic"i*pant</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>A participator; a
partaker.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q><qex>Participants</qex> in their . . . mysterious rites.</q>
<rj><qau>Bp. Warburton.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Participantly</ent>⟦br⟧
